\c 42 Bhuku 2 (Mapisarema 42-72) Chishuwo chomutapwa kushumira Jehovha patemberi Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; rwiyo rwe- Mashiri rwavanakomana vaKora. 42 1 Senondo inotakwairira hova dzemvura, Saizvozvo mweya wangu unokutakwairirai imi Mwari. 2 Mweya wangu une nyota kuna Mwari, iye Mwari mupenyu, Ndichasvika riniko ndionekwe naMwari? 3 Misodzi yangu zvakanga zviri zvokudya zvangu masikati nousiku, Pakutaura kwavo zuva rose kwandiri vachiti, "Mwari wako aripiko?" 4 Ndinorangarira zvinhu izvi, ndichidurura mweya wangu mukati mangu, Zvokuti ndaienda navazhinji, ndichivatungamirira kuimba yaMwari Nezwi rokufara nokurumbidza, k*U.â€˜ Nalkkt NaktaxWn. xmt.zze(*.o 5 Unoshuwireiko, mweya wangu? Unoshaiwa rugare neiko mukati mangu? Tarira kuna Mwari; nokuti ndichazomurumbidza hangu,
